	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hey, saying this now, I am a huge newbie at EQ. But I do have many friends that are EQ junkies and are willing to help me. A Shaman is what I am going to start out with but maybe start a warrior cause tanking looks fun. What is the best Class &amp; Race for shamans in low levels and what stats/skills should I looks to build on?<br>&nbsp;<br>hiya bietch</td></tr>
